`,o.jsxs(r.li,{children:["Bakes in the registry address via ",o.jsx(r.code,{children:'option_env!("CONTRACTS_REGISTRY_ADDR")'}),". This is a compile-time constant-- the address of the on-chain ContractRegistry is embedded directly in the contract bytecode."]}),`
